      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This specialized carpet of flying always measures 10 feet by 10 feet. When it's in flight, its passengers are shielded from wind and extreme temperatures as if inside a tiny hut (though without creating an opaque, immobile sphere). In addition, once per day while the carpet of comfort is on the ground, a command word transforms the carpet into an opulent silk tent that, other than its appearance, is equivalent to a secure shelter.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, overland flight, secure shelter, tiny hut</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>People Of The Sands",
